<tal:block replace="nothing"
 xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
 xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
 xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"/>
 
 <tal:block define="dummy python: request.RESPONSE.setHeader('Content-Type', 'text/css;; charset=utf-8')"/>
 
 /*========================================================================================
 WebSite_viewAgentWorklistRenderer CSS.
 
 ========================================================================================*/
 .tabbertab a.action_number{
 text-decoration: underline;
 font-weight: bold;
 font-size: 1.2em;
 }
 
 .tabbertab ul{
 list-style: none;
 }
 
 .search_tab img{
 margin-right: 25px;
 }
 
 #search {
 float:left;
 vertical-align:middle;
 margin:0px !important;
 }
 
 #search button {
 background-color:inherit;
 border:0pt none;
 color:inherit;
 cursor:pointer;
 margin-left:0pt;
 margin-right:2px;
 margin-top:1px;
 padding:0pt;
 position:relative;
 vertical-align:middle;
 display:inline;
 
 /* margin:0 !important;
 padding:0 !important;
 background-color:inherit;
 border:0pt none;
 color:inherit;
 cursor:pointer;
 display:inline;
 height: 28px;*/
 }
 
 #search button .image {
 background-repeat:no-repeat;
 display:block;
 height:22px;
 width:22px;
 background-image: url('img/search.png');
 /* width: 22px;
 height: 22px;
 padding-bottom: 9px;
 padding-left:22px;
 background-repeat: no-repeat;*/
 }
 
 #search button .description {
 display:none;
 }
 
 
 .application_folder{
 float: left;
 margin-right: 20px;
 background-image: url(img/folder2.png);
 height: 30px;
 padding-left: 30px;
 padding-top: 15px;
 background-repeat:no-repeat;
 vertical-align:middle;
 text-decoration: underline;
 
 }
